title: Windows 10 Insider Preview 11082 ISO (x64 only)
description:
Windows 10 Insider Preview 11082 released on 16 December to the fast ring.

This is NOT an official ISO. However, I created it using the ESDtoISO tool. It used the update that Windows Update downloaded and turned it into a valid ISO file that works like any legit one. If you have any trouble with it, simply revert the changes made. Please let me know how this works for you. I tried it and it's completely safe on my side
